ll over skin with brush, sponge or fingertips—starting at center of face. Build your way to customizable coverage.","foundation");
INSERT INTO product (id, brand, product_name, price, website_link, tags,image_link, product_description, product_type) values("541","smashbox","Full Exposure Waterproof Mascara","22.0","http://www.smashbox.com/", "","https://www.smashbox.com/media/images/products/388x396/sbx_sku_54401_388x396_0.jpg","Sometimes emotions run high in our L.A. photo studio. We developed this long-wearing, waterproof mascara to handle teary moments, rainy days—even a dip in the pool! It’s a high-impact, high-gloss, fiber-rich product that looks flawless and stays put for 10 hours. It also delivers length, volume and thickness without clumping, smudging or flaking out. Swipe on instant drama and face up!Flip brush vertical to literally paint mascara on individual lashes. Specialty brush lengthens, curls & volumizes No clumps, no flakes; sweat & humidity resistant Starting at the base of lashes, sweep mascara up and out.
INSERT INTO product (id, brand, product_name, price, website_link, tags,image_link, product_description, product_type) values("540","smashbox","Full Exposure Mascara","22.0","http://www.smashbox.com/", "","https://www.smashbox.com/media/images/products/388x396/sbx_sku_37089_388x396_0.jpg","During high-profile shoots in our L.A. photo studio, we need to sweep on big, glossy lashes—fast. We infused this patent-leather formula with olive-oil complex to deliver insta-soft lashes and bring you the same fluttery fabulosity at home. When it comes to volume, our mantra is “crank it up.” Every swipe gives you fiber-rich length and thickness without clumps, flakes or smudges.Flip brush vertical to literally paint mascara on individual lashes. Big, tapered brush grabs lash at root for ultra-coverage Glossy fibers sculpt lashes up and out No clumping, smudging or flaking Starting at the base of lashes, sweep mascara up and out.
INSERT INTO product (id, brand, product_name, price, website_link, tags,image_link, product_description, product_type) values("539","smashbox","Indecent Exposure Mascara","22.0","http://www.smashbox.com/", "","https://www.smashbox.com/media/images/products/388x396/sbx_sku_68232_388x396_0.jpg","Created for extreme close-up shots in our L.A. photo studio, no lash can hide with this extreme lengthening formula that takes lashes from barely there to make-‘em-stare.Kick out corner of lashes with micro-tip for a falsie effect. Micro-defining brush nabs every lash Wavelength fibers stretch with each stroke No clumping, smudging or flaking Move brush in zigzag motion to coat lashes from base to tip.
INSERT INTO product (id, brand, product_name, price, website_link, tags,image_link, product_description, product_type) values("537","smashbox","Photo Finish Lash Primer","22.0","http://www.smashbox.com/", "","https://www.smashbox.com/media/images/products/388x396/sbx_sku_68234_388x396_0.jpg","Here's the rule in our L.A. photo studio: No shoots without our primer! This innovative formula lifts lashes to new heights, amps up volume and makes mascara last longer.Refresh and revive midday lashes with primer and layer on fresh mascara. Dual-sided brush/comb coats and separates Preps and amplifies for more mascara pay-off Layer under or over mascara Apply from root to tip of lashes with grooved bristle side of brush and then define and separate with comb.
